-----
Requirements:
-----
macOS 

-----
Configure
-----
Modify the name in flowers.sh Jordana Nahum to the macOS contact name you wish to messaage
Modify install.sh with the crontab schedule you want to run the script to send your hunny sweet nothings
currently the cron is setup to run friday at 1pm each week

Have fun and now you do not have to worry about sending sweet messages manually. Good work!!!
